               <p>ISSAC WOODHOUSE. I am <rs id="t18170219-101-viclabel558" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-101-victim836 t18170219-101-viclabel558"></join> to Mr. Ricketts, who lives at Hertford. On the 4th of January, my cart was in <placeName id="t18170219-101-crimeloc559">Wentworth-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18170219-101-crimeloc559" type="placeName" value="Wentworth-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18170219-101-crimeloc559" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-101-off556 t18170219-101-crimeloc559"></join>. My coat was in the cart, and a table cloth of my master's was in the pocket. I lost it between seven and eight o'clock in the morning.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170219-101-person839">
                  RICHARD 
                  WALLY
